    "description": "<br><br>这是一款第一人称模拟游戏，你将经营一家百货公司。<br>将你简陋的商店扩张为一家百货巨头。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089150/extras/97f7577783f0c18dee9ec543fc519068.poster.avif?t=1750239511\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089150/extras/97f7577783f0c18dee9ec543fc519068.webm?t=1750239511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089150/extras/97f7577783f0c18dee9ec543fc519068.mp4?t=1750239511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >商店流程</h2><br>与头部品牌签订合同，用游戏内的电脑订购新产品，拆开包装，将产品放入你的商店，并为你的产品设定价格。<br>在商店中设定产品价格时考虑市场价格，让客户满意。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089150/extras/26eb8bd3156eb49ac63d279df0df06f8.poster.avif?t=1750239511\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089150/extras/26eb8bd3156eb49ac63d279df0df06f8.webm?t=1750239511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089150/extras/26eb8bd3156eb49ac63d279df0df06f8.mp4?t=1750239511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >产品</h2>请确保你的客户在商店中能找到他们想要的商品。<br>不断扩大你的产品数量让你的客户满意。<br>衬衫、夹克、裤子、运动衫、连衣裙、T 恤、鞋子、帽子等等……<br>注意市场价格并在价格便宜时购买更多产品。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089150/extras/ff25b7bda694ec627e9b011223aa40e5.poster.avif?t=1750239511\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089150/extras/ff25b7bda694ec627e9b011223aa40e5.webm?t=1750239511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089150/extras/ff25b7bda694ec627e9b011223aa40e5.mp4?t=1750239511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >顾客</h2>设置足够数量的收银台和试衣间，减少顾客的等待时间。<br>扫描产品并收取现金或刷卡付款。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089150/extras/bf20ea19e5eb25a1ba49ede8f8382b35.poster.avif?t=1750239511\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089150/extras/bf20ea19e5eb25a1ba49ede8f8382b35.webm?t=1750239511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089150/extras/bf20ea19e5eb25a1ba49ede8f8382b35.mp4?t=1750239511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >扩张和新员工</h2>通过升级商店和提高预算来扩大你的商店和仓库。<br>雇佣库管来填满货架。<br>购买更多收银机并雇佣新收银员，以尽量减少收银台的长队并减少顾客的等待时间。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089150/extras/e119dc4f1d77b3f10c39e16d81342c4e.poster.avif?t=1750239511\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089150/extras/e119dc4f1d77b3f10c39e16d81342c4e.webm?t=1750239511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089150/extras/e119dc4f1d77b3f10c39e16d81342c4e.mp4?t=1750239511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
